---------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Messaging
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------
- enables distributed communication
- must be loosely coupled

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Technologies / Implementations / Patterns
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------
- JMS       / ActiveMQ      / Point-to-Point, Pub-Sub
- AMQP      / RabbitMQ      / Pub-Sub
- Pub Sub   / Redis         / Pub-Sub
- STOMP     / Websockets    / Push technology

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Spring Serialization
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------
- provide a MessageConverter implementation

- Messages are Objects -> use Jackson2JsonMessageConverter
- Messages are Strings -> use SimpleMessageConverter

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Spring Message interface
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------
- generic wrapper for any Java object
- consists of headers and a payload